description:
For some reason Airbnb decided to call this a new listing. It actually isn't, if you wish to see my reviews, here is the link: https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/10209118

It's a decent size studio with a separate kitchen. Gets plenty of sunlight morning till late afternoon. Looks out to the street.

Couple blocks east is the Carl Schultz park by the river. 15 minutes walk to Central Park. Laundry with wash and fold services around the corner. All sorts of restaurants and stores around the block.

5  minute walk to the new Second Ave Q line, 10 minutes to both 4-5-6 train station on 86th and Lexington Avenue.
name: Cozy studio
